criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of diplegic CP (Rosenbaum et al., 2007);

          -  GMFCS levels I, II, and III;

          -  aged between 6 and 25 years;

          -  bilateral surgery.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  other diagnosis than cerebral palsy;

          -  severe mental retardation (IQ < 50).
